  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064870/extras/f73b223388d31405a54c34c72ee45b7f.avif?t=1739893278\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064870/extras_big/f73b223388d31405a54c34c72ee45b7f.avif?t=1739893278 width=800 height=300 /></span><br><br>You come to consciousness with a terrible headache and realize that you are sitting in a cage. You don’t understand where you are and how you got here. But you definitely understand that you need to get out of here urgently...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064870/extras/20b3ecec349b8cd9070d9dfe2d67b39e.avif?t=1739893278\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064870/extras_big/20b3ecec349b8cd9070d9dfe2d67b39e.avif?t=1739893278 width=800 height=300 /></span><br><br>You have to solve a lot of puzzles and learn the story of a serial killer, face fear and escape from a ghost...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064870/extras/421d008cec172c2407367d7ebe04c624.avif?t=1739893278\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064870/extras_big/421d008cec172c2407367d7ebe04c624.avif?t=1739893278 width=800 height=300 /></span><br><br>Good luck!",
